\left(1 + \displaystyle{m\over n}x\right)^{-\left(n+m\right)/2} & $x >
0$ \cr
\cr
0 & otherwise
}>>>,
<<<
@example
 f(x, m, n) = 
                                                         (- n) - m
                                                         ---------
                    n n/2       n + m   n/2 - 1  n x         2
